msgctxt "56_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "Thank you for all of your help, Akiyama-san. I still can't believe I'm a number one hostess!"
msgstr "Gracias por toda su ayuda, Akiyama-san. ¡Todavía no puedo creer que soy la hostess número uno!"

msgctxt "68_Player"
msgid "I just gave you a little advice. You did all the hard work."
msgstr "Yo solo te di un empujoncito. El trabajo duro lo hiciste tú."

msgctxt "80_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "Oh no... I couldn't have done it without you."
msgstr "Ay, no... Jamás lo habría logrado sin su ayuda."

msgctxt "92_Player"
msgid "So, do you think you're going to be able to patch things up with your dad?"
msgstr "Entonces, ¿crees que vas a poder hacer las paces con tu papá?"

msgctxt "104_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "No way! He's as stubborn as a mule. Once he digs in his heels, there's no changing his opinion!"
msgstr "¡Ni hablar! Es terquísimo. ¡Cuando se le mete algo a la cabeza, no hay quien lo haga cambiar de opinión!"

msgctxt "116_Player"
msgid "You sometimes get customers at the club who are about your father's age. You seem to get along with them well enough."
msgstr "A veces vienen al club clientes que tienen la edad de tu papá, más o menos. Se te ve que te entiendes bien con ellos."

msgctxt "128_Player"
msgid "Why is it so different with your father?"
msgstr "¿Por qué es tan diferente la cosa entre tú y tu papá?"

msgctxt "140_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "Because he's my dad! I mean, for one, my customers are actually nice to me."
msgstr "¡Pues porque es mi papá! O sea, para empezar, mis clientes sí me tratan bien."

msgctxt "152_Player"
msgid "They're nice to you because you're not their daughter. They probably don't treat their own kids like they treat you at the club."
msgstr "Te tratan así porque no eres su hija. Seguro que a sus propios hijos no les dan el mismo trato que a ustedes ahí en el club."

msgctxt "164_Player"
msgid "Your father acts the way he does because he loves you. It's different than just talking to someone over drinks."
msgstr "Tu viejo se porta así porque te quiere. No es igual que platicar con alguien mientras tomas unos tragos."

msgctxt "176_Player"
msgid "You really should try and see things from his perspective."
msgstr "Deberías tratar de ponerte en sus zapatos."

msgctxt "188_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "200_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "Maybe the next time I have a customer around my father's age, I'll ask him how he feels about all this."
msgstr "Igual la próxima vez que venga un cliente de la edad de mi papá, le preguntare qué opina de todo esto."

msgctxt "212_Player"
msgid "I think you might learn something. Good luck."
msgstr "Quién sabe, capaz que aprendés algo. ¡Échale ganas!"

